column2: select top # m.mangaID, m.catalog_ra, m.catalog_dec, f.objID, f.ra, f.dec into mydb.mangafirst from mangatarget as m, first.PhotoObjAll as f cross apply dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n join PhotoObj AS o on o.objID = n.objID cross apply dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (f.ra, f.dec) AS nf join o on objID = nf.objID
